// ============================================
// YAADBOOKS - COMPLETE PRISMA SCHEMA
// Jamaica-First Accounting System
// ============================================
// 
// Design Principles:
// - Multi-tenant: All business data scoped to companyId
// - Audit Trail: createdAt, updatedAt, createdBy on all models
